    stem: 'A company runs a Java application in an on-premises data center. The application is not currently containerized but the company plans to migrate it to the AWS Cloud and modernize the application into a containerized deployment. A CI/CD pipeline should also be created to automate application updates. Which solution can a DevOps engineer use to meet all these requirements?',
